info.name: Magical Princess Minky Momo: Hold on to Your Dreams
info.description: After the events of the 1st series, Fenarinarsa continues to drift from Earth, so the King asks for help from the kingdom, Marinarsa, to send their daughter, Momo (Who is identical to the 1st one) to Earth to regain humanity's faith in their dreams.

moreInfo.japanese: 魔法のプリンセス　ミンキーモモ（夢を抱きしめて）
